title: Cal football notes: Daniel Lasco works to regain confidence
text:
Photo: John Storey / Special To The Chronicle Running back Daniel Lasco at Cal Football practice at Memorial Stadium in Berkeley, Calif., on Friday, August 7th, 2015. Running back Daniel Lasco at Cal Football practice at Memorial...
Back in August, Cal players voted Daniel Lasco a captain for the second straight year. His selfless, diligent approach had endeared him to the program more than any touchdown run.
